		<page mustlisten="false" obfuscate="false" length="29283">
			<text><![CDATA[The weather changes with the seasons and months. There are usually four seasons in a year:
spring, summer, autumn and winter.   	
When it is summer in the northern hemisphere, in Europe for example, it is winter in the southern hemisphere, in Australia and South America. When it is winter in Paris, the people in Rio de Janeiro celebrate Carnival outside in the streets. 
In some regions of the world there is also a dry season and a rainy season.]]></text>
