		<page mustlisten="false" obfuscate="false" length="20584">
			<text><![CDATA[It is spring in the Hel peninsula in Poland.  The weather is mild. The birds are back after winter. It often rains and the grass is green. The leaves on the trees are green, too. The lighthouse is red. The water in the bay is grey. There are no waves. It is calm.]]></text>
