		<page mustlisten="false" obfuscate="false" length="29387">
			<text><![CDATA[It is summer in Santa Cruz de Tenerife. The weather is hot. The sun shines every day. 
The sky is blue. The water in the ocean is blue, too. There are some clouds in the sky. 
The temperature of the air can be 30 or 35 degrees C. The days are long and the nights are short. The sun rises early and sets late.]]></text>
