		<page mustlisten="false" obfuscate="false" length="34925">
			<text><![CDATA[It is autumn in Gdynia in Poland. There are waves breaking on the sandy beach. 
It is often windy. The Baltic sea can be rough. The sky is overcast with clouds. 
It rains sometimes. The temperature of the air is about 15 degrees C. The leaves on the trees are turning yellow and brown. The season is called the fall in America because the leaves fall from the trees. The birds are preparing to migrate to warmer regions of the world. ]]></text>
