			<text><![CDATA[It is winter in Jastarnia in the Hel peninsula in Poland. The weather is very cold. It often snows. There is sometimes ice in the bay. The temperature of the air can fall below zero. 
The days are short and the nights are long. The sun rises late and sets early.]]></text>
